nodes.text: The Zealots of Psusan was a female cult based on Kuat, led by a High Priest. They could be recognized by a spiritual tattoo on the abdomen, surrounding the navel. In 22 BBY they enjoyed a surge of popularity on Coruscant.
Members included Nyrat Agira, Rosha Vess and likely Khaleen Hentz and Breela. In 22 BBY the High Priest was Scri Oscuro.
